            "title": "美伊戰火露曙光！伊朗外長啟程巴基斯坦斡旋 荷姆茲封鎖壓力仍升溫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bOtWAQ7rvmBIJ6hAiNCD2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/d4d59484fb843d974b6e63fc5389719b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%88%B0%E7%81%AB%E9%9C%B2%E6%9B%99%E5%85%89-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7%E5%95%9F%E7%A8%8B%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E6%96%A1%E6%97%8B-%E8%8D%B7%E5%A7%86%E8%8C%B2%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E4%BB%8D%E5%8D%87%E6%BA%AB-140006331.html",
