        {
            "title": "美股漲勢會否後繼乏力?Yardeni發表看法",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkDpYjpDmIaIJWpMGtgkUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA8400B_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 儘管油價突破100美元、軟體板塊動盪以及中東局勢未解,但根據Yardeni Research的分析,自3月31日開始的美股漲勢依然保持完好,因為美國經濟持續通過壓力測試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週四晚間,布蘭特原油再度攀升,此前有報導稱,伊朗首席談判代表Mohammad Bagher Ghalibaf因伊斯蘭革命衛隊內部強硬派的干預而退出和平談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,Yardeni Research指出,期貨市場仍顯示未來12個月油價將大幅下跌,而且情緒指標顯示多空比率\"尚未高到足以讓我們對股市漲勢感到擔憂\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-20496344-84b9-3a8a-9310-c3342ad8adb0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">軟體股週四遭受重創,ServiceNow因中東交易延遲而下跌18%,IBM則因Red Hat增長放緩而下跌7%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟宣布為資深員工提供自願買斷計劃,加劇了市場憂慮,Yardeni形容這是\"一次大規模內部重組,旨在從傳統軟體轉向純AI業務\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者正在轉向硬體,半導體板塊獲得支撐。英特爾在強勁財報公布後,盤後一度飆升20%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟數據提供了進一步保證。失業救濟申請人數仍遠低於長期平均水平,4月份的快閃PMI表現強勁,服務業和製造業指數均顯示廣泛加速。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過,Yardeni提醒,製造業增長的一部分反映的是預期供應短缺前的預防性庫存建設,而非真正的需求加速,供應商交貨時間惡化至2022年中以來的最差水平。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%BC%B2%E5%8B%A2%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E5%BE%8C%E7%B9%BC%E4%B9%8F%E5%8A%9B-yardeni%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-133201516.html",
